FeedPackage.Description: This package is a WCF Appender for log4net. The interface has two modes, client rendering and server rendering. This is to allow you the option to postpone the rendering of the event data if you want to be able to change rendering configuration without redeploying your clients. Example configurations can be found at the project site.
